longBusinessSummary: Asia Commercial Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the retail and wholesale of watches in Hong Kong, the People's Republic of China, and Switzerland. The company operates in two segments, Sale of Watches and Properties Leasing. It is also involved in the assembly and marketing of gold and jewelry watches; property holding, development, investment, and leasing activities; and brand development business. The company was incorporated in 1990 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.
